gaffer

# Runtime shared library co-located beside the binary by release
# builds (build-release links with a co-location-only rpath; dev builds
# use a build-dir rpath and don't drop it here).
Gaffer.Runtime.so
Gaffer.Runtime.dylib
Gaffer.Runtime.dll

# Build-time copies of canonical files. internal/mcpserver/resources/
# telemetry-info.gen.md is `cp TELEMETRY.md` produced by the
# `_resources` recipe so the MCP resource always matches what the
# worker serves at https://telemetry.gaffer.kurrent.io/cli.
internal/mcpserver/resources/*.gen.md
